{
  "uid": "aidra-tipcue-replay",
  "title": "AIDRA — Tip & Cue Replay",
  "description": "Autonomous re-tasking chains: every time AIDRA detects a low-confidence vessel cluster, it queues a re-observation cue (T0 → Cue → T1). Each row links to a side-by-side visual replay with SAR thumbnails before/after and confidence uplift. This is the SatCen tender extra.",
  "tags": ["aidra", "tipcue", "tasking", "autonomy", "wow"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "editable": true,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "liveNow": false,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "time": { "from": "now-30d", "to": "now" },
  "timepicker": {
    "refresh_intervals": ["10s", "30s", "1m", "5m"],
    "time_options": ["1h", "6h", "24h", "2d", "7d", "30d", "90d"]
  },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "status",
        "type": "custom",
        "label": "Cue status",
        "description": "Filter cues by lifecycle status.",
        "query": "all,pending,executing,completed,failed",
        "current": {"text": "all", "value": "all"},
        "options": [
          {"text": "all",       "value": "all",       "selected": true},
          {"text": "pending",   "value": "pending",   "selected": false},
          {"text": "executing", "value": "executing", "selected": false},
          {"text": "completed", "value": "completed", "selected": false},
          {"text": "failed",    "value": "failed",    "selected": false}
        ],
        "multi": false
      },
      {
        "name": "api_base",
        "type": "textbox",
        "label": "API base URL",
        "description": "Base URL of the AIDRA REST API used for thumbnails and replay links. Edit in the toolbar (or override via ?var-api_base=...) when running this dashboard against a non-production deployment.",
        "query": "https://aidra-api.uliber.com",
        "current": {"text": "https://aidra-api.uliber.com", "value": "https://aidra-api.uliber.com"},
        "hide": 0
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 100,
      "title": "How to read this dashboard",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 24, "h": 4 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Tip & Cue** is AIDRA's autonomous re-tasking loop. When a pipeline run produces a low-or-moderate-confidence detection cluster in a zone of interest, the evaluator queues a `cue` to **re-observe** the same area in the next satellite pass. Each row below is a chain `T0 → Cue → T1`.\n\n- **T0** = the original execution that triggered the cue.\n- **Cue** = the re-tasking entry (target zone, priority, reason).\n- **T1** = the re-observation execution (when the scheduler runs the cue).\n\nClick **▶ Open replay** to see a visual side-by-side comparison: SAR thumbnails of the triggering detections vs. the confirming detections, with confidence uplift and latency metrics. This is the SatCen tender extra: the satellite chasing its own findings."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Cues in window",
      "description": "Total cues created in the selected time range, filtered by the Cue status variable above (default 'all' shows full history).",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 4, "w": 5, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
          "rawSql": "SELECT COUNT(*) AS cues\nFROM tasking_queue\nWHERE created_at BETWEEN $__timeFrom() AND $__timeTo()\n  AND ('$status' = 'all' OR status = '$status')",
          "format": "table",
          "editorMode": "code"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "blue", "value": null }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "title": "Pending now (live backlog)",
      "description": "Cues currently waiting to be executed — ignores the time range and the status filter so the operator always sees the live re-tasking backlog.",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "x": 5, "y": 4, "w": 5, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
          "rawSql": "SELECT COUNT(*) AS pending\nFROM tasking_queue\nWHERE status = 'pending'\n  AND attempts < max_attempts\n  AND (cooldown_until IS NULL OR cooldown_until < NOW())",
          "format": "table",
          "editorMode": "code"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 1 },
              { "color": "orange", "value": 10 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 50 }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Completed (re-observed)",
      "description": "Cues whose re-observation has been executed.",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "x": 10, "y": 4, "w": 4, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
          "rawSql": "SELECT COUNT(*) AS completed\nFROM tasking_queue\nWHERE created_at BETWEEN $__timeFrom() AND $__timeTo()\n  AND status = 'completed'",
          "format": "table",
          "editorMode": "code"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }] }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Avg triggering detections",
      "description": "Mean number of detections per cue (the cluster size that fired the re-tasking).",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "x": 14, "y": 4, "w": 5, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
          "rawSql": "SELECT ROUND(AVG(cardinality(triggering_detections))::numeric, 1) AS avg_dets\nFROM tasking_queue\nWHERE created_at BETWEEN $__timeFrom() AND $__timeTo()\n  AND ('$status' = 'all' OR status = '$status')",
          "format": "table",
          "editorMode": "code"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "blue" }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Top zones by cues",
      "description": "Which zones of interest fire the most re-tasking events.",
      "type": "piechart",
      "gridPos": { "x": 19, "y": 4, "w": 5, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
          "rawSql": "SELECT COALESCE(target_zone, 'unknown') AS zone, COUNT(*) AS cues\nFROM tasking_queue\nWHERE created_at BETWEEN $__timeFrom() AND $__timeTo()\n  AND ('$status' = 'all' OR status = '$status')\nGROUP BY target_zone\nORDER BY cues DESC\nLIMIT 8",
          "format": "table",
          "editorMode": "code"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "right" },
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": true },
        "pieType": "donut"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Tip & Cue chains (click ▶ Open replay)",
      "description": "Each row is a re-tasking cue. Click '▶ Open replay' to see the visual T0 → Cue → T1 walkthrough with SAR thumbnails before / after and confidence uplift.",
      "type": "table",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 8, "w": 24, "h": 16 },
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
          "rawSql": "SELECT\n    '${api_base}/api/tipcue/replay/' || t.id || '.html' AS \"replay\",\n    t.created_at                                  AS \"cue_at\",\n    t.status                                      AS \"status\",\n    COALESCE(t.target_zone, '—')                  AS \"zone\",\n    t.priority                                    AS \"prio\",\n    cardinality(t.triggering_detections)          AS \"trigger_dets\",\n    COALESCE(t.confirmed_detections, 0)           AS \"confirmed\",\n    COALESCE(t.result_status, t.status)           AS \"result\",\n    t.attempts                                    AS \"attempts\",\n    COALESCE(t.reason, '')                        AS \"reason\",\n    t.id::text                                    AS \"tasking_id\"\nFROM tasking_queue t\nWHERE t.created_at BETWEEN $__timeFrom() AND $__timeTo()\n  AND ('$status' = 'all' OR t.status = '$status')\nORDER BY t.created_at DESC\nLIMIT 100",
          "format": "table",
          "editorMode": "code"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": { "align": "auto", "filterable": true }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "replay" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "custom.cellOptions", "value": { "type": "text" } },
              { "id": "custom.width", "value": 140 },
              {
                "id": "links",
                "value": [
                  { "title": "Open replay (new tab)", "url": "${__value.text}", "targetBlank": true }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "mappings",
                "value": [
                  { "type": "regex", "options": { "pattern": ".*", "result": { "text": "▶ Open replay" } } }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "cue_at" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "unit", "value": "dateTimeAsIso" },
              { "id": "custom.width", "value": 200 }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "status" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "custom.cellOptions", "value": { "type": "color-text" } },
              {
                "id": "mappings",
                "value": [
                  { "type": "value", "options": {
                    "pending":   { "text": "pending",   "color": "yellow" },
                    "executing": { "text": "executing", "color": "blue" },
                    "completed": { "text": "completed", "color": "green" },
                    "failed":    { "text": "failed",    "color": "red" }
                  } }
                ]
              },
              { "id": "custom.width", "value": 110 }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "prio" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "custom.width", "value": 70 },
              {
                "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                "value": { "type": "color-background", "mode": "gradient" }
              },
              {
                "id": "thresholds",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "absolute",
                  "steps": [
                    { "color": "blue",   "value": null },
                    { "color": "yellow", "value": 1 },
                    { "color": "red",    "value": 2 }
                  ]
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "trigger_dets" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "custom.width", "value": 120 }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "confirmed" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "custom.width", "value": 110 }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "attempts" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "custom.width", "value": 90 }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "tasking_id" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "custom.hidden", "value": true }]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "footer": { "show": false }
      }
    }
  ],
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": { "type": "grafana", "uid": "-- Grafana --" },
        "enable": true,
        "hide": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "name": "Annotations & Alerts",
        "type": "dashboard"
      }
    ]
  }
}
